cs.ET, cs.AR, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper discusses the design and analysis of an analog neural training accelerator using resistive memories, which falls under the category of emerging technologies (cs.ET). The paper also involves circuit and device analysis, which could be categorized under computer architecture (cs.AR). The focus on neural networks and pattern recognition suggests a connection to the sub-categories of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of optimization and architecture-level studies suggests a possible connection to systems and control (cs.SY).
